verbose_text: All the seven cases presented at an extensive clinical stage and showed a poor prognosis with the survival time ranged from 3 to 11 months.3, 4, 5, 6 We present the first case of a laryngeal NMC patient treated with intensity modulated radiation therapy (IMRT) and traditional Chinese medicine (TCM) after local resection, which exhibits long-time survival potential.
